---
// Lessons section with three cards and how it works
---

<section id="lessons" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-4 text-center">
      Online Guitar Lessons
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[#a0a0a0] text-lg text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Personalized instruction designed to deepen your musicality, technique, and understanding of Brazilian guitar traditions.
    </p>

    <!-- Lesson Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#3a3a3a] hover:border-[#009739] transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#009739]/10">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#009739] to-[#007a2e] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-3">
          Foundations & Feel
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
          Master timing, groove, and right-hand technique. Build the rhythmic foundation that makes Brazilian music breathe.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#3a3a3a] hover:border-[#fedd00] transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#fedd00]/10">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#fedd00] to-[#d4bc00] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1a1a1a]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-3">
          Harmony & Brazilian Vocabulary
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
          Explore chord voicings, harmonic movement, and the rhythmic patterns that define bossa nova, samba, and choro.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#3a3a3a] hover:border-[#002776] transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#002776]/10">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#002776] to-[#001a55] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-3">
          Improvisation & Expression
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
          Develop phrasing, tone, and musical vocabulary. Learn to listen, respond, and express yourself authentically.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How it Works -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-[#3a3a3a] mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-6">How It Works</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#009739] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[#f5f5f0] font-semibold mb-1">1:1 Zoom Sessions</h4>
            <p class="text-[#a0a0a0]">Live, interactive lessons tailored to your goals and skill level</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#009739] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[#f5f5f0] font-semibold mb-1">Flexible Scheduling</h4>
            <p class="text-[#a0a0a0]">Weekly recurring sessions or book as your schedule allows</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#009739] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[#f5f5f0] font-semibold mb-1">Personalized Practice Plan</h4>
            <p class="text-[#a0a0a0]">Custom exercises, recordings, and resources between sessions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <a 
        href="#calendar" 
        class="inline-block bg-[#009739] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#007a2e] transition-all transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#009739] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#1a1a1a] font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg"
      >
        Schedule a Lesson
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
